		<a href="/docs/api/lithium/2.0.x/lithium" class="symbol-segment">lithium</a>\<a href="/docs/api/lithium/2.0.x/lithium/net" class="symbol-segment">net</a>\<a href="/docs/api/lithium/2.0.x/lithium/net/http" class="symbol-segment">http</a>\<a href="/docs/api/lithium/2.0.x/lithium/net/http/Media" class="symbol-segment">Media</a>::asset()		</h1>

		<section class="under">
															<div class="tags">
